Description:
    Generates a contact page that creates an activity in the WebCRM and prefills
    the form if an user is logged in. The given homepage is extended with a
    configuration link to the contact page.

Example:
    `rails generate cms:component:contact_page`
    `rails generate cms:component:contact_page --homepage_path=/website/en`

    CMS: obj_class ContactPage
    CMS: attribute title (string)
    CMS: attribute body (html)
    CMS: attribute show_in_navigation (enum)
    CMS: attribute crm_activity_type (string)
    CMS: attribute contact_page_link (linklist)
    CMS: attribute redirect_after_submit_link (linklist)
    CMS: <path to homepage>/_configuration/contact
         "contact_page_link" added to object class "Homepage"
    CRM: Activity type 'contact-form' with attributes 'email' and 'message'
    Gems: "valid_email"